\begin{MintedVerbatim}[commandchars=\\\{\}]
UI layer: routes + components
├─ App.tsx
│  ├─ routes + providers
│  └─ Screens
│     ├─ Dashboard / Wallet / Mining / ...
│
Data layer: React Query hooks
├─ useApi.ts
│  ├─ useQuery / useMutation
│  ├─ cache keys + invalidation
│
HTTP boundary
├─ ApiClient (Axios)
│  └─ one method per endpoint
│
Rust node
└─ /api/admin/* endpoints
\end{MintedVerbatim}
